related_questions.question: What are the requirements to work at Dollar Tree?
related_questions.snippet: Typically at 18 Years of Age While the retail chain offers several avenues for entry-level employment, the minimum hiring age imposed by Dollar Tree requires applicants to stand 18 or over. The 18-year-old minimum also requires applicants to hold high school diplomas or GED equivalents, in most cases.
